<ext_description linkend="shape_composition_mim">
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: composite_group_shape_aspect
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.composite_group_shape_aspect">
<p>

A <b>composite_group_shape_aspect</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> that implements the
ARM concept of  <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_group_shape_element"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: composite_unit_shape_aspect
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.composite_unit_shape_aspect">
<p>

A <b>composite_unit_shape_aspect</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> that implements the
ARM concept of  <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_unit_shape_element"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: composite_shape_element_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.composite_shape_element_constraint">
<p>
The <b>composite_shape_element_constraint</b> rule constrains the use of a  <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> when it is used as a composite shape element or as an implementation of the ARM object <express_ref linkend="Part_feature_grouping:arm:Part_feature_grouping_arm.Part_group_feature"/> or as an implementation of the ARM object <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Composite_shape_element"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: composite_shape_element_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.composite_shape_element_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each  <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> shall be specified as the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> by at least two  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> that have a name of 'composing'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: composite_shape_element_constraint.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.composite_shape_element_constraint.wr:WR2">
Each  <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> shall be at least one other type of  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: shape_element_composing_relationship_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.shape_element_composing_relationship_constraint">
<p>

The <b>shape_element_composing_relationship_constraint</b> rule constrains the use of a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> when it is used as a shape element composing relationship.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: shape_element_composing_relationship_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.shape_element_composing_relationship_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> with a name of 'composing' shall have a <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> that is a  <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: shape_element_constituent_relationship_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.shape_element_constituent_relationship_unique_constraint">
The <b>shape_element_constituent_relationship_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> 
population members, that fill the role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_constituent_relationship"/>, to have
unique <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.related"/> shape elements on each <express_ref linkend="Shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element_relationship.relating"/>  shape element.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.shape_element_constituent_relationship_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> with a name of either 'constituent'
or 'composing' or 'interconnect module terminal surface constituent relationship'
or 'bare die terminal surface constituent relationship'
or 'package terminal surface constituent relationship'
that has a common <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> shall have a unique
<express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> attribute value.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: shape_element_locating_relationship_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.shape_element_locating_relationship_unique_constraint">
The <b>shape_element_locating_relationship_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains <express_ref linkend="shape_dimension_schema:ir_express:shape_dimension_schema.dimensional_location"/>
population members, that fill the role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship"/>, to have
unique <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship.located_shape_element">located_shape_elements</express_ref> on each <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:arm:Shape_composition_arm.Shape_element_locating_relationship.locating_shape_element"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.shape_element_locating_relationship_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref linkend="shape_dimension_schema:ir_express:shape_dimension_schema.dimensional_location"/> that has a common <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/>
must have a unique <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> attribute value.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: subtype_mandatory_composite_shape_aspect
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.subtype_mandatory_composite_shape_aspect">
The <b>subtype_mandatory_composite_shape_aspect</b> rule requires all <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> entities to 
be either <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:mim:Shape_composition_mim.composite_group_shape_aspect"/>, or <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:mim:Shape_composition_mim.composite_unit_shape_aspect"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Shape_composition_mim.subtype_mandatory_composite_shape_aspect.wr:WR1">
<p>
Every instance of <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> shall be either a
<express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:mim:Shape_composition_mim.composite_group_shape_aspect"/> or a <express_ref linkend="Shape_composition:mim:Shape_composition_mim.composite_unit_shape_aspect"/>.
</p>
<note>
Other subtypes of <express_ref linkend="shape_aspect_definition_schema:ir_express:shape_aspect_definition_schema.composite_shape_aspect"/> will form a complex instance with one of the above
designated subtypes.
</note>
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
